{"tid":246451,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財仔主席王瑤賣地賺2,600萬","createTime":"2017-05-17T04:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T05:01:51.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58550eb366bceb5281725f85e315933678d55e81","tid":246451,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"財仔主席王瑤賣地賺2,600萬<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】億元大刁連環成交，其中有財仔界「性感女神」稱號的環球信貸（1669）主席王瑤把6年前買入的灣仔酒店地皮沽出，料賬面賺2,600萬元。<br />\n<br />\n1.2億賣灣仔酒店地<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指出，灣仔慶雲街17至19號地盤，佔地約1,316.5方呎，曾以2億元放售，但零售及旅遊業進入調整期，業主意向價已降至1.6億元，惟最終以1.2億元成交。地盤劃為「住宅（甲類）」地帶，但已獲批興建酒店，商業樓面約16,433方呎，可興建樓高25層連4層平台的酒店大樓，提供78間客房。<br />\n土地註冊處資料，物業由環球物業發展有限公司在2011年以9,400萬元買入，持貨5年，賬面賺2,600萬元，升值27.7%。公司股東王瑤，與環球信貸主席同名，市場料是同一人。記者昨日曾聯絡她，但直至截稿時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n此外，九龍城道42至46號奥斯酒店，傳以約5.8億元成交，以酒店提供約151間房計，每間房作價約384萬元。<br />\n原業主2005年先後斥資共約1,700萬元買入上述土地發展酒店，據悉2013年才開幕。<br />\n舖租持續下跌。旺角彌敦道603至609A號新興大廈地下8A號舖，面積約2,200方呎，以約48萬元租出，呎租218元，比較2015年簽訂舊租59萬元，新租金比兩年前租金平11萬元或18.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170517/large/17bm11pz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170517%2Flarge%2F17bm11pz.jpg&h=b567e472&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24d2cfb71bd23792bacc0c1c15142abd1bc5909e","tid":246451,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"強姦我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca00566c83a172fb17cea8282d3889c204d5b73","tid":246451,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強姦我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6875284096fc65bd1e5eb9037b56cffe4b91ea1c","tid":246451,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強姦我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係都我先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdec57532b59b64046c80865ae4b8c37742ce292","tid":246451,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"我唔揀飲擇食嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}